<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>You Have Been Invited - Artist Management System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">Artist Management System</div>

      <h1>You have been invited!</h1>

      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>
        You have been invited to join <strong><%= companyName %></strong> as an <strong><%= role.replace('_', ' ').toUpperCase() %></strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Please click the button below to accept your invitation, set up your password, and access your account.
      </p>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="<%= inviteUrl %>" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #888888">
        This invitation link expires in <strong><%= expiresInDays %> days</strong>. Please accept it before then.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #888888">
        If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:<br/>
        <a href="<%= inviteUrl %>" style="color: #888888; word-break: break-all;"><%= inviteUrl %></a>
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #888888">
        If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Artist Management System</p>
        <p>© 2026 All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
